versions.localizedDescription:
# V 1.3.0 Release

🔍 Sora Search Integration
Global search now includes results from Sora modules. Easily add supported add-ons from the Sora Library. https://sora.jm26.net/library/

📺 Stremio Add-ons Support
Now supports Stremio Subtitles and Live TV add-ons for a richer streaming experience.

# V 1.2.24 Release

This release focuses on resolving various bugs that affected the user experience. The following issues have been fixed:
- **Streamer Pro key deletion**: The Streamer Pro key would sometimes get deleted without warning, causing the loss of premium features. This issue has been resolved and the key is now securely stored.
- **Downloads failure**: Downloads would not work if the user signed in with a personal free dev account. This issue has been resolved and downloads are now available for all users.
- **Casting update**: Casting would not update the “Continue watching” section, making it difficult to resume watching later. This issue has been resolved and the section is now updated accordingly.
- **Casting links**: When casting a movie or a TV show, the links list would not appear, preventing the user from choosing the best quality or source. This issue has been resolved and the links list is now visible.
- **Subtitles persistence**: Subtitles would still show even when the user disabled them in the settings screen. This issue has been resolved and subtitles are now turned off as expected.

修正了頁數篩選器僅在同時指定了頁數的上下限時才正常運作的問題。

1. fix: App not responding when accessing a gallery recursively.
ギャラリーを再帰的にアクセスするとアプリが反応しなくなる不具合を修正。
修正了在遞迴存取畫廊時 App 失去回應的問題。

2. fix: App lock gets bypassed under some circumstances.
アプリロックがある状況下でバイパスされる不具合を修正。
修正了 App 鎖定功能在某些情況下被繞過的問題。

eh ギャラリーホストでのページング不具合を修正。

2. fix: App icon Developer layout issue.
アプリアイコン「デベロッパ」のレイアウト不具合を修正。
修正了應用圖示「開發者」的佈局顯示問題。

フィルター除去数表示設定を追加。

ex ギャラリーホストでのページング不具合を修正。
修正了 ex 畫廊下的翻頁問題。

# Bugfixes

1. fix: Unexpected behaviors when accessing ex gallery host in any display modes but Compact.
「コンパクト」以外の表示モードで ex ギャラリーホストにアクセスすると発生する予期せぬ動作を修正。
修正了以「緊湊」顯示模式外存取 ex 畫廊出現的非預期行為。

2. refactor: Conditions to show the Create New button in EhSetting page.
EhSetting 画面での「新規作成」ボタンの表示条件をリファクタリング。
重構了 EhSetting 頁面的「新增」按鈕的顯示條件。

プレビューの最初の一組しか読み込まない不具合を修正。
修正了預覽在第一組圖像之後不載入的問題。

1. fix: Unexpected behaviors when the gallery host set to ex.
ex ギャラリーホストでの予期せぬ動作を修正。
修正了 ex 畫廊下出現的非預期行為。

1. fix: Unexpected behaviors on iOS or iPadOS 16 devices.
iOS・iPadOS 16 デバイスでの予期せぬ動作を修正。
修正了 iOS、iPadOS 16 裝置上的非預期行為。

2. fix: Will not start loading automatically when navigating to PreviewsView issue.
プレビュー画面へ遷移する際、読み込みが自動的に始まらない不具合を修正。
修正進入預覽頁面時不自動開始載入的問題。

3. refactor: Reduce the file size of releases.
リリースのファイルサイズを減らす。
減小發佈的檔案大小。

apps.name: CercubePlus (Legacy)
apps.subtitle: CercubePlus but for iOS 12!
apps.localizedDescription:
Unfortunately, AltStore can not handle two (or more) applications that have the same bundle ID (uYouPlus, CercubePlus and CercubePlus (Legacy)). I have no other choice except to modify the bundle ID of CercubePlus (Legacy). Thus, you won't be able to install CercubePlus (Legacy) directly through AltStore. You still can download the IPA like normal though.

Full infomation about CercubePlus (Legacy) is available on my Github: https://github.com/qnblackcat/CercubePlus/tree/iOS-12/

Credits: Please keep the Credits if you re-up CercubePlus (Legacy)! 
- Alfhaily for Cercube.
- Galactic-Dev for the original iSponsorBlockLegacy, @Luewii for his fork of iSponsorBlock (which works in jailed mode).
- PoomSmart for YouRememberCaption, YTClassicVideoQuality, YTNoCheckLocalNetwork, YTSystemAppearance, and Return YouTube Dislike.
- level3tjg for YTNoHoverCards.

Known issues:
- YTUHD is removed because most iOS 12 devices don't support VP9 codec (Hardware restriction).
- iOS 12 doesn't have the built-in Picture in Picture mode like iOS 14+, so YouPiP must be removed as well.
- Hide Cast button may not work.
- YouPiP (iOS 14.0 - 14.4.2): due to Apple's fault, you may encounter the speedup-bug as described here. The bug also happens when you try to play multi-sources of sound at the same time. Enable Legacy PiP is a workaround. Note that Legacy PiP removes UHD quality and breaks the default video quality feature of uYou. Use it at your own risk!

apps.name: Spotify++ (Old)
apps.subtitle: The original Spotilife tweak, along with other tweaks
apps.localizedDescription:
USE THIS IF YOU DO NOT LIKE THE NEW ONE OR IF ITS NOT WORKING

I would highly recommend you use the new Spotify tweak as it has been updated to work on newer Spotify versions and is currently being updated. However this tweak may stop working in the near future as it is an old version.



Spotify++ contants a tweak that activates Premium. As well as a number of tweaks to customise the UI and improve the overall user experience.

Here are the following tweaks:

• Spotilife - Premium for free.

• Sposify - A Tweak to customize your Spotify App UI and expand functionalities.

• Volify - Adds a volume slider to Spotify.

• SpotifyAllowSetting - Allows you to access all of the settings in Spotify that are normally disabled when someone else is playing music from another device.

• SpotifyNoPodcasts - Hides Podcasts from from Home and Library

• SpotifyHighQuality - Enables 'Very High' Quality in Audio Quality settings

•TrueShuffle - Enables true random shuffling (Spotify prioritizes Songs you have listened to more often by default)

• Spoticentre - Centres the song/artist in now playing (Only working on some devices)



NOTE

The ‘Car’ setting has been replaced with the sposify tweak settings so unfortunatley you cannot change car settings - all good tho, nobody use that shi anyways, and when car view enables when u in the car, just click ‘turn off car view’ at the top right corner.


All tweaks are injected by myself, WuXu, and ensured to be working perfectly ;)
